channel.description:
Jaime Murray turns up the charm, fogging the truth in a way Warehouse 13 fans have come to love and loathe her for. She makes situations unpredictable and fun. Nowhere else has composer Bear McCreary's influence been felt as strongly as in the pauses during this exchange; he impregnates them with subtle meaning that deepens the exchange..
Les nodmocrates et les libraux avaient convoqu, chacun leur tour, les journalistes mercredi pour dnoncer le ministre de la Dfense, Peter MacKay, et le premier ministre Harper qui ils reprochent d'avoir menti au Parlement et aux Canadiens, leur cachant le vritable prix de ces avions. Mais si les libraux rclament la dmission du ministre et le dpart du premier ministre, les nodmocrates, eux, se contentent de demander M. Harper de faire ce qu'il faut faire, sans prciser davantage..
I even took it seriously when I was an angstfilled teenager and I have the journals and stories to remind me. But when the weight of my independence started to distract me and consume the time it takes to sit and write, I decided writing would be a luxury I would enjoy when I am old. And I focused on my career and on "living a rich life" that would be give me something to write about some day..
"The reason why companies bundle functionality and security updates is that users hate having to go through the pain of updating," said Pescatore. "Customers like fewer updates." What users dislike, he added, is when a vendor hides security fixes in a larger update. Microsoft's been guilty of that in the past when it's issued fixes but not disclosed the underlying vulnerabilities, perhaps in an attempt to keep the bug count artificially low..
Zuckmayers Stck behandelt im zweiten und dritten Akt die Zeit um den spektakulren berfall und im ersten Akt eine fiktive Vorgeschichte, die zehn Jahre vorher spielt. Neben kleineren nderungen (so wird Voigts Geburtsort in die Nhe der Wuhlheide verlegt, sodass Voigt Berliner Dialekt spricht), besteht der Hauptunterschied des Stckes zur Wirklichkeit wohl in der Stilisierung Voigts zum edlen Ruber'. So bernimmt Zuckmayer die (wenig glaubhafte) Selbstdarstellung Voigts, wonach das Motiv fr seinen berfall ausschlielich der Erwerb eines Passes gewesen sei, den er dringend brauchte, um wieder ein normales Leben beginnen zu knnen.
